full_title: Parking Lot by Mustard & Travis Scott
title: Parking Lot

description.plain: Parking Lot marks the second collaboration between DJ Mustard and Travis Scott. The duo first collaborated on their 2016 hit single ‘Whole Lotta Lovin.’ ‘Parking Lot’ is the first single released for DJ Mustard’s upcoming album FAITH OF A MUSTARD SEED. The song explores themes of sex and cars while also referencing Travis' roots back in his hometown of Missouri City, Texas.
